Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.21,0:02:25.08,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,give me an answer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.70,0:02:31.49,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,不器用でぎこちないほど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:34.49,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,愛しく始まるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.79,0:02:36.60,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,give me an answer
